---
layout: base.njk
title: MIST
description: Eval-driven infrastructure for AI systems. MatchSpec, InferMux, SchemaFlux, TokenTrace.
permalink: /
---

<div class="hero">
  <h1>See through the mist.</h1>
  <p class="tagline">Eval-driven infrastructure for AI systems.</p>
  <div class="install"><code>go get github.com/greynewell/mist-go</code></div>
</div>

<div class="section-heading">Tools</div>
<div class="card-grid">
  {% for tool in site.tools %}
  <div class="card">
    <h3><a href="{{ tool.url }}">{{ tool.name }}</a></h3>
    <p>{{ tool.description }}</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">
      <a href="{{ tool.docsUrl }}" style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.78rem;">Docs →</a>
      {% if tool.tutorialsUrl %}&ensp;<a href="{{ tool.tutorialsUrl }}" style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.78rem;">Tutorials →</a>{% endif %}
    </p>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<div class="section-heading">Use Cases</div>
<div class="card-grid">
  {% for uc in site.useCases %}
  <div class="card">
    <h3><a href="{{ uc.url }}">{{ uc.title }}</a></h3>
    <p>{{ uc.description }}</p>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<div class="section-heading">Built with MIST</div>
<div class="card-grid">
  {% for project in site.builtWith %}
  <div class="card">
    <h3><a href="{{ project.url }}">{{ project.name }}</a></h3>
    <p>{{ project.description }}</p>
    {% if project.post %}<p style="margin-top: 0.75rem;"><a href="{{ project.post }}" style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.78rem;">Read the writeup →</a></p>{% endif %}
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
